snippet.title: NEW SONG OUT! (notifications may have glitched and I can't make community posts yet)
snippet.description:
Just notifying you that I posted a new song on my channel. I had a bit of a panic when after I posted it was only playing through one of my headphones and I made the video private before I realized it was just my headphones and not the audio of the video. Doing this may mess with being able to access the video through the notification link so I just wanted to fill you guys in, in case it wasn't working. I would have just reposted it to make sure but I spent a substantial amount of time manually putting in subtitles via the YouTube creator studio so I was going to have to re-do it and I was so not into that.

check out my new song "CANCER" here!👉 https://youtu.be/-EoF4OcmXdY
